                    <span>I have read lot of good books on OOAD and patterns like Design Patterns, Refactoring, Analysis Patterns etc. I wish I read this book along with Design Patterns long back. If you are starting new with patterns... read this.... just 150 pages. If the cost seems high, buy an used one.</span>
                  
              
